      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-sky-900 mb-4">Best Places to Visit in Alibaug</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Alibaug is known for its mix of beaches, forts, and scenic coastal views. Popular places include Nagaon Beach for water sports, Alibaug Beach for sunsets, Kashid Beach for peaceful outings, and Murud-Janjira Fort for history lovers.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
        Staying near Nagaon Beach allows you to cover most attractions within a short drive.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
