      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Nagaon is one of the most preferred areas in Alibaug because of its clean beach, easy access to water sports, and central location. Compared to crowded Alibaug town, it offers a quieter and more comfortable stay experience.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        For a deeper comparison, read our <a href="/why-smart-travelers-choose-nagaon" class="font-semibold text-sky-700 hover:underline">why-smart-travelers-choose-nagaon</a> guide before you book.
